enhanced_by.reason: The processSchemaQueue method relies on the cache and processingQueue being populated by the addSchema method.
The getOrAddSchema method can also populate the cache and processingQueue, which are essential for the processSchemaQueue method to function.
Both processSchemaQueue and getChangedSchemas methods interact with the cache to retrieve processed schemas, making them useful for constructing assertions.
Both processSchemaQueue and PendingChanged.logResolved() involve logging resolved operations, which can be used to verify the correct execution flow.
